'''Ammar n tudfirt amikṛuwan''' (s [[Taglizit|Tegnizt]]: cosmic microwave background radiation)  d  [[azenzar azrurdekran]] yettilin deg yal tama d teɣmert n [[Asedday|usedday]] s yiwen n udwas d usegder, [[taẓɣelt|taẓɣelt-is]] tegda 2.725° C.<br/> 
Tanfalit tamatant tga d «'''izenzaren udfiren'''» yennumken izenzaren izrurdekranen ɣef waci i d-illa wanza (ttbut) ɣef tilin-ines deg yal adeg deg tallunt akken ur yettwazmer ara ad yili usemyif kra n uɣbalu yettwanalin deg-s. Izenzaren uddiren i d-izgan s deffir n tɣult n tayyugin timikṛuwanin '''izenzaren udfiren n usedday''' s usrag n wazal-is meqqren deg [[tassnamdelt tasengamt]] akken i tettwasemma daɣen s «izenzaren 3 C» s usrag n teẓɣelt-is d tneẓẓi n tfasa-ines yudren.<br/>
Mi ara ad nwali ɣer tegnawt s [[amsaddas|umsaddas]] ad nẓer istumen meqqren gar n [[itri|yitran]] d [[amazellaw|imazellawen]] i teddel tebrek, dɣa d anecta yettwasemman s wammar udfir. Maca mi ara ad neǧǧ amsaddas s wacu id nettaney yis [[tafat|tafat timeẓrit]] w ad nwali s umsaddas izemren ad iẓer [[tayyugin tisedrarin]] ad aɣ-d-isseknew tafat timdellest yeččarayen tudfirt-nni, yerna izenzaren-a ur ttbeddilen ara seg wadeg ɣer wadeg niden, maca ttnfufuden s ugdu deg yideggan n usedday yakk. Issek (taqacuct) n uzenzar-a tettili deg tjumma n [[teɣzi n tayyugt]] 1,9 mm ayen yegdan 160,2 n imelyaṛen [[Hertz]]  (160&nbsp;GHz). Izenzaren-a ttwasnirmen-d sɣur n sin n inagmayen [[Arno Allan Penzias]] d [[Robert Woodrow Wilson]] deg useggas n [[1964]] ayen id ten-yeǧǧan ad awin [[Arraz n Nobel di tsengama]] deg useggas n [[1978]] 


